001package io.github.ai4ci.config;
002
003import org.immutables.value.Value;
004
005import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonSubTypes;
006import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonSubTypes.Type;
007import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonTypeInfo;
008import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonTypeInfo.Id;
009
010/**
011 * Interface for defining modifications to model configurations and parameters.
012 *
013 * <p>
014 * This interface provides polymorphic support for different types of model
015 * modifications through JSON type deduction, allowing for flexible
016 * configuration updates during model execution and setup phases.
017 *
018 * @param <X> the type of object being modified
019 */
020@JsonTypeInfo(use = Id.DEDUCTION)
021@JsonSubTypes(
022        { @Type(PartialExecutionConfiguration.class),
023                        @Type(PartialStochasticModel.class),
024                        @Type(PartialPhenomenologicalModel.class),
025                        @Type(PartialMarkovStateModel.class),
026                        @Type(PartialSetupConfiguration.class) }
027)
028public interface Modification<X> {
029        /**
030         * Returns the modified object instance itself.
031         *
032         * @return the modified object instance
033         */
034        @Value.NonAttribute
035        X self();
036}
